foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: The Annual Peace Corps’ FOIA Report for 2007 included Privacy Act requests that the Agency conducted a Privacy Act search that the Agency processed completely and exclusively under the Privacy Act. Therefore, the number in Column 1 does not match the number of “Requests Pending as of End of Fiscal Year” from last year’s Annual FOIA Report.
